nnel protein.'),(423,'ARO:3000504','golS','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000451','regulates ARO:3000786','GolS is a regulator activated by the presence of golD, and promotes the expression of the MdsABC efflux pump.'),(424,'ARO:3000506','MexR','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000219,ARO:3000451','part_of ARO:3004048,part_of ARO:3004080,regulates ARO:3000386','MexR is the repressor of the MexRAB-OprM operon. Mutant forms of mexR result in up-regulation of efflux pump system MexAB-OprM.'),(425,'ARO:3000507','rifampin-resistant RNA polymerase-binding protein','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000185,ARO:3000383','','Proteins which have been experimentally shown to protect RNA-polymerase from rifampin inhibition.'),(426,'ARO:3000508','gadX','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000451','regulates ARO:3000788,regulates ARO:3003838','GadX is an AraC-family regulator that promotes mdtEF expression to confer multidrug resistance.'),(427,'ARO:3000510','Staphylococcus mupB conferring resistance to mupirocin','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000446','confers_resistance_to_drug ARO:3000554','An alternative isoleucyl-tRNA synthetase conferring resistance to mupirocin.'),(428,'ARO:3000515','evgSA','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000451','regulates ARO:3000373,regulates ARO:3000788','EvgSA is a two-component regulatory system that regulates MdtEF and EmrKY expression for multidrug resistance. EvgS is a sensor protein that phosphorylates the regulatory protein EvgA, though EvgA can be phosphorylated by other methods when it is overexpressed.'),(429,'ARO:3000516','emrR','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000451','regulates ARO:3000344','EmrR is a negative regulator for the EmrAB-TolC multidrug efflux pump in E. coli. Mutations lead to EmrAB-TolC overexpression.'),(430,'ARO:3000517','rifaximin','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000157','','Rifaximin is a semi-synthetic rifamycin used to treat traveller`s diarrhea. Rifaximin inhibits RNA synthesis by binding to the beta subunit of bacterial RNA polymerase.'),(431,