antibiotic sensitive dihydrofolate reductase','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000714','targeted_by ARO:3000171,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000188,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000269,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000284,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000337','Dihydrofolate reductase synthesizes the co-enzyme tetrahydrofolic acid, which is also an essential precursor in the de novo synthesis of the DNA nucleotide thymidine.'),(635,'ARO:3000746','mepR','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000451','regulates ARO:3000026','MepR is an upstream repressor of MepA in Staphylococcus aureus. It is part of the mepRAB operon.'),(636,'ARO:3000747','mef','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:0010002','confers_resistance_to ARO:0000000','Mef efflux pumps are MFS-type transporters that confer macrolide resistance in Streptococcus pneumoniae.'),(637,'ARO:3000748','subunit of efflux pump conferring antibiotic resistance','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000159','','Subunits of efflux proteins that pump antibiotic out of a cell to confer resistance.'),(638,'ARO:3000749','beta-lactam sensitive penicillin-binding protein','antibiotic_resistance','ARO:3000709','targeted_by ARO:0000044,targeted_by ARO:3000007,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000008,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000011,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000015,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000043,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000054,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000056,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000058,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000059,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000060,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000061,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000062,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000063,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000064,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000070,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000073,targeted_by_drug ARO:0000078,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000170,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000550,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000632,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000633,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000634,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000635,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000636,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000637,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000638,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000639,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000640,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000641,targeted_by_drug ARO:3000642,targe